18:09.494 --> 18:10.494
Gorgeous.

18:12.440 --> 18:13.440
Yeah.

18:14.365 --> 18:15.423
You know, Chris,

18:16.434 --> 18:20.234
I've been thinking a lot lately
about us and...

18:20.271 --> 18:21.568
Me too.

18:21.606 --> 18:24.541
- I already feel closer to you.
- You do?

18:25.211 --> 18:29.705
