You should really try this.

18:59.444 --> 19:01.139
It's succulent. It's...

19:01.179 --> 19:04.806
- Tommy?
- It's absolutely delectable. This...

19:04.947 --> 19:05.705
Tommy?

19:05.716 --> 19:07.183
