out of the floor.

24:26.900 --> 24:29.793
These pieces were embedded
in a chair over there between two customers.

24:30.074 --> 24:32.167
Nolan, what do you think?

24:33.043 --> 24:35.409
Look delicious.
What about it?

24:39.150 --> 24:41.812
Amanda, I don't think so

24:41.852 --> 24:43.479
but let's find the sugar cookies.

24:43.521 --> 24:46.456
Oh, thanks for the confidence.

24:46.490 --> 24:47.821
Go away.

25:27.698 --> 25:28.892
She did it!

25:30.134 --> 25:31.897
Something weird is going on.
Amanda!

25:32.903 --> 25:34.302
I'm upstairs, Nolan.

25:37.541 --> 25:40.408
I'm in here.
And hands off the dolls.

25:41.509 --> 25:42.509
How is this?

25:43.410 --> 25:44.510
For what?

25:44.511 --> 25:47.480
Buying plates.
Uptown.

25:47.518 --> 25:49.418
Rewind.

25:49.453 --> 25:51.683
Tom offered
to buy us plates.

25:51.722 --> 25:53.849
It would be rude not to accept.

25:54.040 --> 25:55.427
Oh, Tom!

25:56.227 --> 25:58.127
We have to have plates.

25:58.162 --> 26:02.098
I think that psycho chick from yesterday,
she left at least three, right?

26:02.132 --> 26:05.761
That's Ruth, Howard and Bill.
Three. We're safe.

26:05.803 --> 26:07.763
- How is this?
- No.

26:09.673 --> 26:13.575
Okay, so, when I get there,
what do I talk to him about?

26:13.611 --> 26:16.670
You saw him and you know me and
you know how I tend to run on when I get nervous.

26:16.671 --> 26:18.692
And I know I'm gonna be nervous
in a place like that.

26:18.716 --> 26:21.316
Amanda, relax. Just be yourself.

26:26.091 --> 26:27.718
No. What? Please!

26:27.758 --> 26:31.027
See? This is what I'm afraid of.

26:31.061 --> 26:33.052
Come on, Nolan, help me.

26:33.097 --> 26:36.933
I mean, you're a guy, right?
What are guys interested in?

26:36.968 --> 26:39.734
- Sex.
- Sex?

26:39.770 --> 26:41.829
I can't talk about sex.

26:42.907 --> 26:45.432
Well, there's sports cars and money...

26:45.476 --> 26:48.274
No, we only think about sex.

26:48.312 --> 26:51.907
No, that can't be right. There has to be
something else we can talk about.

26:51.949 --> 26:53.610
Yeah, I saw that on Dateline.

26:53.651 --> 26:57.712
The average man
thinks about sex 238 times a day.

26:58.722 --> 27:01.290
That means they
think about sex all day.

27:01.324 --> 27:02.951
Pretty much.

27:02.992 --> 27:04.721
Maybe that applies to you.

27:04.761 --> 27:06.058
Pretty much.

27:06.095 --> 27:09.155
Look, you know how guys
are always adjusting their belts?

27:09.199 --> 27:10.325
Oh, don't tell me this.

27:10.366 --> 27:13.335
Nolan, stop! I'm not listening.

27:13.369 --> 27:14.847
Well, that's when
they're thinking about it.

27:14.871 --> 27:16.338
Check it out for yourself.

27:16.372 --> 27:18.670
Oh, my god.
Why did you tell me this?

27:18.708 --> 27:21.805
Now every time I see somebody doing that
it's gonna be in my head. Forever.

27:21.845 --> 27:22.735
Thank you.

27:22.775 --> 27:23.940
You asked.

27:24.948 --> 27:27.007
- Well, I gotta go.
- Wait.

27:31.721 --> 27:32.721
Really?

27:35.291 --> 27:36.724
Yeah, yeah, that one.

28:11.995 --> 28:13.484
- Ramos
- Tom

28:14.740 --> 28:16.659
- No, no, no.
- What?

28:17.433 --> 28:19.645
Round ones should stay on the top,
square ones on the bottom.

28:19.669 --> 28:21.330
Oh. See?

28:21.371 --> 28:26.040
Wait, wait! Don't adjust. Never.
Just admire.

28:27.510 --> 28:29.842
That's beautiful.

28:29.879 --> 28:33.014
- Gook job, man!
- Thanks, thanks.

28:33.049 --> 28:34.840
God, what would I do
without you?

28:39.856 --> 28:42.154
Excuse me. Hi.

28:42.992 --> 28:46.223
Do you know where
I can find Tom Bartlett?

28:46.224 --> 28:47.224
Yeah, he was just here.

28:48.940 --> 28:50.140
There he is.

28:51.540 --> 28:52.727
Thank you.

28:57.640 --> 28:58.800
I owe you.

28:58.841 --> 29:01.207
No, I'll just grab this last one and...

29:01.244 --> 29:03.405
Please let it lie.

29:03.446 --> 29:05.437
No, I'm sorry.

29:05.481 --> 29:07.449
If you just allow me
I think I can...

29:07.483 --> 29:09.178
Sorry.

29:10.787 --> 29:12.414
Please, please let me...

29:13.856 --> 29:15.255
Hi.

29:15.291 --> 29:17.919
Oh, no. Ramos will take care of this.
Have Laura help you.

29:17.960 --> 29:18.960
Thanks.

29:21.230 --> 29:22.993
I guess this makes us even.

29:24.901 --> 29:28.530
Yeah, I guess you could call this even.

29:28.571 --> 29:29.571
I'm really sorry.

29:29.672 --> 29:31.765
No, no. It's a nice coincidence.

29:31.808 --> 29:34.440
- Do you shop here a lot?
- Me? No. Never.

29:37.447 --> 29:40.541
I thought you said you'd
replace the plates.

29:40.583 --> 29:43.143
Didn't you? That's why I'm here.

29:43.186 --> 29:45.245
Sure, I thought you'd send the bill.

29:45.288 --> 29:47.222
Don't you sell plates?

29:47.256 --> 29:49.850
Yeah. China is on fourth floor.

29:49.892 --> 29:52.588
And do all these elevators
go to fourth?

29:52.628 --> 29:55.188
Pick one, press four.

29:55.231 --> 29:56.596
Right.

29:57.600 --> 29:58.692
Thanks.

29:58.735 --> 29:59.963
You're welcome.

30:01.637 --> 30:03.662
- Sorry.
- Don't worry about that.

30:05.074 --> 30:07.700
There is a beautiful new line,
from Italy...

30:07.740 --> 30:11.940
- It's really... it's beautiful.
- What?

30:11.980 --> 30:13.892
Facing this way it'll be on the top
shelf. It'll be on your right.

30:13.916 --> 30:16.214
I can't hear you.

30:18.654 --> 30:20.986
Never mind, I - I'll show you.

30:30.800 --> 30:32.062
Four...

30:35.138 --> 30:38.301
